title: Patrick Reed has clubs and will travel
text: Photo: Ahn Young-joon, AP United States' Phil Mickelson reacts after chipping onto a green during his singles match against International team player Charl Schwartzel of South Africa at the Presidents Cup golf tournament at the Jack Nicklaus Golf Club Korea, in Incheon, South Korea, Sunday, Oct. 11, 2015. United States' Phil Mickelson reacts after chipping onto a green... NAPA, Calif. (AP) — The Presidents Cup followed the end of a long season for Patrick Reed, and he still has a long way to go.
